description:
This week, ANN features several stories including how an Adventist university is sharing the Gospel through music; a Fellowship day in Ireland brings together people from different cultures and backgrounds; and friendship saves the lives of two women in Brazil. 

For more Adventist news, subscribe to our Youtube channel. 

ANN is the official news channel of the Seventh-day Adventist Church. For all things Adventist news, visit adventist.news
